Description:
You are at the base of the great staircase, but in front of you there are two colossal automatons blocking your way.

The automatons do not attack you immediately, they seem to be on the defensive and their only intention is to protect the staircase.

No matter how hard you look at it, your only option is to defeat them in order to continue.
DescriptionAction: How do you want to proceed?
